e,"overview":"During the holiday season, when the animals of the Central Park Zoo are preparing for Christmas, Private, the youngest of the penguins notices that the Polar Bear is all alone. Assured that nobody should have to spend Christmas alone, Private goes into the city for some last-minute Christmas shopping. Along the way, he gets stuffed into a stocking","genre_ids":[16,35,10751],"popularity":1.5139,"vote_count":385,"poster_path":"/gOVdfrRfzQjYwezOxIap13j05d8.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-23","vote_average":6.852,"backdrop_path":"/gdJ6j1hmt6dQgObWxDJAHUb58o6.jpg","original_title":"The Madagascar Penguins in a Christmas Caper","original_language":"en"},{"id":10293,"adult":false,"title":"Pauline at the Beach","video":false,"overview":"Marion is about to divorce from her husband and takes her 15-year-old niece, Pauline, on a vacation to Granville. There, she meets an old love...","genre_ids":[18,10749,35],"popularity":0.8383,"vote_count":243,"poster_path":"/kjC8I6fvchcxPBdh4bw4w8Px8ue.jpg","release_date":"1983-03-23","vote_average":6.986,"backdrop_path":"/dahbqgB8m8vtPQclAEiAfGnE4Ix.jpg","original_title":"Pauline à la plage","original_language":"fr"},{"id":470639,"adult":false,"title":"I'm in Love With My Little Sister","video":false,"overview":"Yori and his twin sister Iku used to be very close as children but lately Yori has grown colder toward Iku and is always eager to stay away from her. Iku was confused by Yori's attitude. Actually Yori is in love with Iku and that forbidden love is causing Yori sleepless nights since Yori and Iku are sharing the same room with bunk beds. Yori tried to ease his intense desire for Iku by bedding Iku's best friend. He had even applied to attend a boarding school in another city to take him far away from Iku. Yori lost his resolve to stay quiet about his feelings when Iku started to talk about having a boyfriend and going on dates. Now Yori want to have his little sister and he confessed. Iku loves her big brother and wanted them to stay together, so Iku is willing to anything to keep them together. But Yori wanted to have Iku as a lover, not as a sister loyal to her twin.","genre_ids":[10749,16,18],"popularity":0.5583,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/fRdxgR85XX5BAWsPETWW7t3UfdV.jpg","release_date":"2005-05-18","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":"/iHfNZMfP9q6mudJdJTNqMQWXQCZ.jpg","original_title":"僕は妹に恋をする","original_language":"ja"},{"id":470703,"adult":false,"title":"Body Jack: Sublime Separation","video":false,"overview":"A high schooler fulfills a lifelong fantasy after a high-tech device lets him slip into the body of his childhood crush's best friend.","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.5044,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/yEzTCkU2eURPpxXBTFp6rHmkVJ5.jpg","release_date":"1987-01-28","vote_average":4.4,"backdrop_path":"/tq7zViUEXnVzMfaYEeVEE0zuZT3.jpg","original_title":"ボディジャック 楽しい幽体離脱","original_language":"ja"},{"id":10475,"adult":false,"title":"Factotum","video":false,"overview":"This drama centers on Hank Chinaski, the fictional alter-ego of \"Factotum\" author Charles Bukowski, who wanders around Los Angeles, CA trying to live off jobs which don't interfere with his primary interest, which is writing. Along the way, he fends off the distractions offered by women, drinking and gambling.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.8221,"vote_count":208,"poster_path":"/qfuqZHaAFiC4N8natPXojrpXR2y.jpg","release_date":"2005-04-25","vote_average":6.151,"backdrop_path":"/k41nJTWy18zAWv0mGqXOfLCb7Ct.jpg","original_title":"Factotum","original_language":"en"},{"id":10476,"adult":false,"title":"Hustle & Flow","video":false,"overview":"With help from his friends, a Memphis pimp in a mid-life crisis attempts to become a successful hip-hop emcee.","genre_ids":[80,18,10402],"popularity":1.6811,"vote_count":426,"poster_path":"/yO5QTMZ2Oex6mwsgJuwRuINGuOQ.jpg","release_date":"2005-07-22","vote_average":7.141,"backdrop_path":"/d4ZrRcwEPmLQvOCyrSdWw5NglGB.jpg","original_title":"Hustle & Flow","original_language":"en"},{"id":10486,"adult":false,"title":"My Father the Hero","video":false,"overview":"A teenage girl on vacation in the Bahamas with her divorced father tries to impress a potential boyfriend by saying that her father is actually her lover. Remake of the 1991 French film Mon père, ce héros.","genre_ids":[10751,35,10749],"popularity":1.0783,"vote_count":211,"poster_path":"/qOP80oUZRTT7EsV7EZA9aBa95dQ.jpg","release_date":"1994-02-04","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/sHfxJXELZHyFIt6H8sfCnJkdFMu.jpg","original_title":"My Father the Hero","original_language":"en"},{"id":10426,"adult":false,"title":"Friday After Next","video":false,"overview":"Craig and his cousin Day-Day have finally moved out of their parents' houses and into their own crib, working nights at a local mall as security guards. When their house is robbed on Christmas Eve they set out to track down the culprit.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":1.8852,"vote_count":450,"poster_path":"/sxHFGPKLWj9e3aaA6wGVxghoiPE.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-22","vote_average":6.358,"backdrop_path":"/bfnQPbcmPAXO2QmDONalx4vNWPB.jpg","original_title":"Friday After Next","original_language":"en"},{"id":279926,"adult":false,"title":"Christmas Miracle in Caufield, U.S.A.","video":false,"overview":"Based on the true story of coal miners who became trapped underground in a cave-in on Christmas Eve, 1951.","genre_ids":[18,10770],"popularity":0.3909,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/kyIlTd2pbCE8aBFJGwASz7Bk0gi.jpg","release_date":"1977-12-26","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/AiRc3NN1Ix8oXgEBtoOBWcm2eRO.jpg","original_title":"Christmas Miracle in Caufield, U.S.A.","original_language":"en"},{"id":10437,"adult":false,"title":"The Muppet Christmas Carol","video":false,"overview":"A retelling of the classic Dickens tale of Ebenezer Scrooge, miser extraordinaire. He is held accountable for his dastardly ways during night-time visitations by the Ghosts of Christmas Past, Present and Future.","genre_ids":[10402,35,10751,14,18],"popu